.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, green, ivory, yellow, blue
There 5 different types of food: apple, asparagus, mango, zucchini, cauliflower
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: lily, iris, bellflower, sunflower, begonia
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, milk, orange-juice, water
5 different pets are kept: dog, fox, zebra, horse, snails

1. the person eating apple is the person who likes red
2. the person eating asparagus is the owner of the dog
3. the person drinking coffee is the person who likes green
4. the person eating mango is the person drinking tea
5. the person who likes green is to the right of the person who likes ivory
6. the person who growslily is the owner of the snails
7. the person who growsiris is the person who likes yellow
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the person eating zucchini is on the far left
10. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the owner of the fox
11. the person who growsiris is to the left or right of the owner of the horse
12. the person who growssunflower is the person drinking orange-juice
13. the person eating cauliflower is the person who growsbegonia
14. the person eating zucchini is to the left or right of the person who likes blue

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Food	|   zucchini	|    mango	|     apple	|    asparagus	|    cauliflower	|
| Color		|    yellow	|      blue	|      red	|     ivory	|     green	|
| Beverage	|     water	|      tea	|      milk	| orange-juice	|     coffee	|
| Flower		|     iris	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| sunflower	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     fox	|     horse	|     snails	|     dog	|     zebra	|
